                Shocking and controversial, ahead of its time, not accepted not only by the public, but even by the artist's colleagues, still evoking extremely contradictory feelings - Picasso's painting "The Maidens of Avignon" ("The Maidens of Avignon") opened up a completely new direction in pictorial art - cubism. Today we will recall some interesting facts related to this world famous work of Pablo Picasso.
